nodes.text: An Imperial technician served aboard the Imperial I-class Star Destroyer Executrix during the battle near the Gulf of Tatooine. Following the battle, the technician informed Moff Wilhuff Tarkin, the Executrix's commander, that the Star Destroyers Compliant and Enforcer had reverted from hyperspace from the Imperial marshaling station at Pii.
The technician was first mentioned in James Luceno's 2014 novel Tarkin.
